This is an audio sample of my new book titled To Make Matters Worse. This clip talks about my neighborhood and how I loved taking a shit in horrible places.

To Make Matters Worse will be available in print on Amazon and other retailers. The audio book will be available on Audible and on CD. www.dannymarianino.com 

Recorded at Arcane Digital Recording Studio in Mesa AZ by Ryan Butler and inspired by a life of idiocy.